<HEADLINE>
FT  28 JAN 92 / World News in Brief: Mrs Mugabe dies
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Sally Mugabe, Ghanaian-born wife of Zimbabwe president Robert Mugabe, died,
aged 60. She was the secretary for the women's league in Mugabe's ruling
Zanu-PF party.
</TEXT>
<PUB>The Financial Times
</PUB>
