<TEXT>
PUBLIC, Malaysia's fourth largest domestic bank, has reported a 28 per cent
rise in pre-tax profit to MDollars 164m (USDollars 63m) last year from
MDollars 128m in 1990.
The group, which has interests in stockbroking and finance, has been active
abroad for the past two years, with acquisitions and investments in a
